## Installation

```console
python3 -m pip install oc_chess_club
```

## Usage

To start the CLI, simply type:

```console
python3 -m oc_chess_club
```

To learn more, please refer to the [documentation](https://pablolec.github.io/oc_chess_club) (:fr:).

